            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>
新的博客使用<a href="http://renard.github.com/o-blog">o-blog</a>搭建，使用的是自已的分枝<a href="https://github.com/tangxinfa/o-blog">tangxinfa-o-blog</a>，我的分枝主要是对原系统做了一定的简化以便适用于创建个人博客，另修复了一些bug（主要是中文相关），可使用以下配置安装我的分枝：
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">

<pre class="src src-lisp">(setq el-get-sources '((<span style="color: #cc99cc;">:name</span> tangxinfa-o-blog
<span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span> <span style="color: #cc99cc;">:type</span> git<span style="color: #f99157; background-color: #515151;"> </span>
<span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #999999; background-color: #2d2d2d;"> </span> <span style="color: #cc99cc;">:url</span> <span style="color: #66cccc;">"https://github.com/tangxinfa/o-blog.git"</span>
